WEBVTT

00:03.987 --> 00:05.628
Welcome to the Mother Court.

00:05.653 --> 00:07.290
Ms. Krissman, I'm on duty today.

00:07.324 --> 00:09.191
TINA: When cases come in,
I e-mail them to you.

00:09.225 --> 00:10.159
Anybody who's new,

00:10.193 --> 00:12.260
this is United States Attorney,
Douglas Delap.

00:12.295 --> 00:14.165
My mother came by for lunch
and wanted to say hi.

00:14.199 --> 00:15.725
Senator Knox. A pleasure.

00:15.726 --> 00:17.727
Calling your mommy is never a power move.

00:17.761 --> 00:19.238
KATE: I don't want fun.

00:19.263 --> 00:21.431
I want challenging, interesting.

00:21.465 --> 00:22.732
You're smart, attractive.

00:22.767 --> 00:23.967
You're a catch.

00:24.001 --> 00:25.869
I'm gonna grab something
to eat if you...?

00:25.903 --> 00:27.370
Think I'm out for this one.

00:27.405 --> 00:28.570
Good night, Kate.

00:31.942 --> 00:33.276
[DOOR OPENS]

00:33.310 --> 00:36.212
[SIREN WAILS IN THE DISTANCE]

00:36.247 --> 00:40.917
[INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS]

00:42.000 --> 00:48.074
